title: Large One Bedroom Section 8 Accepted
posting_body: ['Welcome to Gateway Apartments, our community is a fantastic place to call home!', 'Each apartment includes air conditioning, ceiling fans, multiple spacious closets, FREE off-street parking, on-site card operated laundry and on-site management.', 'Detached garages are also available.', 'Conveniently located just minutes from St. Paul and Maplewood mall, nearby dining, shopping, lakes, and easy highway access.', 'We are a tax credit property which accepts Section 8, GRH, HRA and market rate tenants.', 'Are you ready to make the move to Gateway Apartments?', 'The apartment features air-conditioning, on-site laundry, and modern appliances.', 'LEASING INFORMATION:', 'Security Deposit: One months rent', 'Application Fee: $50 per applicant', 'Pets: Cats allowed', 'Pet Fees: $200 fee, plus additional $200 deposit, plus $25 monthly pet rent', 'Laundry:', 'On-Site card operated Washers, and Dryers.', 'Please call our friendly staff today for more information.', 'show contact info', 'Apply here:', '<URL>']
